{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864054653,"sessionID":"ses_286420526ffemxX9IgFBarLSnp","part":{"id":"prt_d79be7cd80016Y1cvmA0L8CvQv","messageID":"msg_d79be7251001FFA47l5RO2k4Q4","sessionID":"ses_286420526ffemxX9IgFBarLSnp","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-012/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-012\ntitle: 会话存储接口定义\nmodule: pkg/store\nlanguage: Go\nsize: S\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n# Module: pkg/store\n# Language: Go\n# Size: S\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: session-storage-interface\n  description: |\n    Define the session storage interface for the agentcube project.\n    This interface abstracts the storage operations for session data,\n    providing a clean contract for session persistence and retrieval.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - Session storage interface definition\n    - CRUD operations for session data\n    - Interface abstractions for different storage backends\n    - Error handling contracts\n  out:\n    - Concrete storage implementations (separate AR)\n    - Migration logic (separate AR)\n    - Caching layer (separate AR)\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - Interface defines clear CRUD operations for sessions\n  - Interface is agnostic to storage backend\n  - Error types are well-defined\n  - Documentation is complete\n  - Unit tests for interface contracts\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - AR-010: Router 会话管理\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: S\n  story_points: 2\n  days: 1\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_2026041